fields.descriptive_line: A collection of electrotype reproductions of Scandinavian bracteates.
fields.physical_description: A collection of electrotype reproductions of Scandinavian bracteates.
fields.public_access_description: This is a collection of electrotype reproductions of Scandinavian bracteates. Sixty-six are Norwegian, one hundred and thirty-six are Danish, and ninety-three are Swedish. Some of these reproductions, 516 to 581-1873, are in the Metalwork collection.
